title: Chinese frigates cruise in waters near Diaoyu Islands
description: Two Chinese Navy’s frigates were reportedly seen cruising in the waters 80 nautical miles northwest of the Diaoyu Islands, Fuji News Network reported Thursday.
cleanContent: By Yu Runze, Sina EnglishTwo Chinese Navy’s frigates were reportedly seen cruising in the waters 80 nautical miles northwest of the Diaoyu Islands, Fuji News Network reported Thursday.It is for the first time that Chinese Navy’s ships were spotted in the area, said the report.																																																																								|  |
